&lt;h4 id=&#34;java注释&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#java注释&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; Java 注释&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;lt;img src=&amp;quot;&lt;span class=&#34;exturl&#34; data-url=&#34;aHR0cHM6Ly9jZG4uanNkZWxpdnIubmV0L2doL3l1YW5vZXMvaW1hZ2Vob3N0QG1haW4vcGljL2ltYWdlLTIwMjEwMjI3MTUyNjU4MzAwLnBuZw==&#34;&gt;https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/yuanoes/imagehost@main/pic/image-20210227152658300.png&lt;/span&gt;&amp;quot; alt=&amp;quot;image-20210227152658300&amp;quot; style=&amp;quot;zoom:50%;&amp;quot; /&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;
